# Fix Responsive Layout - 21px Overflow Issue

## Problem
The current flex layout causes 21px overflow on the rounded box due to cumulative padding/margins. The solution must be 100% dynamic and resolution-independent.

## Root Cause
- App.tsx Layout has `padding: 24px` on ALL sides
- SearchForm Card has `marginBottom: 24px`
- These fixed values don't account for available space properly
- Need to use pure flex layout with gap instead of margins

